OL,3,CFull list of NHS hospitals declaring a
OL,4,Ccritical incident
OL,6,FSeveral NHS hospitals in England have
OL,7,Fdeclared critical incidents due to
OL,8,Frising demand from winter illnesses
OL,9,Fand the impact of recent severe
OL,10,Fweather.
OL,12,FA critical incident is declared when
OL,13,Fthe level of disruption means
OL,14,Fhospitals are unable to deliver
OL,15,Fcritical services and may not be able
OL,16,Fto operate safely.
OL,18,FThis comes as the number of patients
OL,19,Fin hospitals in England with flu has
OL,20,Fquadrupled in the last month.
